{"tid":750922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「學生獨立聯盟」參與遊行聲援民族黨    約1200人參與遊行","createTime":"2018-07-21T11:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T12:01:43.000Z","uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2dbab18bdcf1f38b9a3386f4180526b24ff02487","tid":750922,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:17:54.000Z","msg":"民陣下午遊行抗議當局計劃以《社團條例》禁止香港民族黨運作，他們由灣仔盧押道遊行到警察總部，之後集會。民陣指有1200人參與，副召集人區諾軒將請願信交予警方代表後，集會結束。<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒表示，有1200人出席是難能可貴，又指民陣反對香港獨立，但容許支持港獨的組織上台發言，是為了證明可以做到「和而不同」，質疑政府為何辦不到，批評當局的做法是破壞香港言論和結社自由。<br />\n<br />\n主張港獨的「學生獨立聯盟」20多名成員亦有參與遊行，民族黨召集人陳浩天則未有現身。"},{"pid":"51eac7f659cfea1d88de928b0c5da94a5aa5600a","tid":750922,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:01:43.000Z","msg":"五毛樓主群龍共舞<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/200139_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F200139_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=0b25d8fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/200140_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F200140_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1f04465b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/200141_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F200141_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f713d6fa&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}